.TH "git-drop" 1
 
.SH NAME
git-drop - safely delete a git branch with interactive confirmation and worktree safety checks
 
.SH SYNOPSIS
git drop <branch>
 
.SH DESCRIPTION
git\-drop \- delete a git branch safely.
 
Ensures that the specified branch is not currently checked out in any worktree. Attempts to delete the branch safely using git branch -d, and falls back to prompting for interactive confirmation before using git branch -D.
